This is Concerto 2.

Automated Installation:
curl get.concerto-signage.org | ruby

OR

Manual Installation:
Run the following commands to get the source code (1 + 2), configure the database (3), install the necessary libraries (4), and setup the database (5).
1. git clone https://github.com/concerto/concerto.git
2. cd concerto
3. cp config/database.yml.sample config/database.yml
2. bundle install
3. rake db:setup

Configure your webserver to point to the Concerto application.
Go the the Concerto URL to setup the initial admin user.

